            "title": "港大發78億債建北都：財政穩健？工程超支？債券安全無肉食、擴建添財務隱憂？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WGDqQstzumw4OBw5Qwq_hw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/28hse_com_210/a3ae31d3e2c13241a9e9c09a2e59989e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
